O(3)
\xi \in \mathfrak{o}(3)
\mathfrak{o}(3) = \{\xi \in M_{3\times 3} : \xi + \xi^T = 0\}
A_p : O(3) \to S^2
\phi \mapsto \phi \cdot p
X_p = \frac{d}{dt}\bigg|_{t=0} \exp(t \xi)(p) = d_e A_p(\xi)
p=(x,y,z)\in S^2
 \xi = \left( \begin{matrix} 0 & 1 & 0 \\ -1 & 0 & 0 \\ 0 & 0 & 0 \end{matrix} \right)
 \begin{align} X_p &= d_e A_p(\xi)\\     &= \xi \cdot p \\     &= \left( \begin{matrix} 0 & 1 & 0 \\ -1 & 0 & 0 \\ 0 & 0 & 0 \end{matrix} \right) \left( \begin{matrix} x \\ y \\ z \end{matrix} \right)  \\ &= y \partial_x - x \partial_y, \end{align}
